{
  "stem": "24171.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But most of the time it was locked.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we start to get typhoid fever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and there was dysentery, you know, because people were going to that thing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was outside, too, a thing, but we start to get sick.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were full of lice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were-- and the things, they had tails.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's how big they were.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and what it was there, kinda like the-- the-- that bathroom, like the hallway.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You couldn't get into it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was impossible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then people start to die, especially the ones that they say-- I was the first one, kind of, from our group who got typhoid fever.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I remember once, I-- when I was sick, I-- I dreamt of my-- my parents, that they giving me the cultured milk, you know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that's kind of sourish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was so good, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Well, anyway, on the zahlappell, it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was raining, too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was in-- in the spring.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And-- and I was-- at that time, I was in the middle.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the girls were a thing, because, you know, I-- I couldn't stay on my feet.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And-- so they were-- when-- when the woman came, the SS woman, to count-- so one would-- you know, my-- my cousin was standing in the front, and she grabbed me backwards, you know, by my-- what I had on.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And-- and the girl-- the-- my niece-- was holding me in the back for that few seconds which she passed by.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then again, I slumped.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I-- I was sitting then, because it wasn't wet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I had the-- a big thing with me, a-- a pot, kind of-- a bowl.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I was sitting on that bowl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I shouldn't sit in-- in the thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So we been sitting there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
